  "title": "CHEF",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibilities:</p><p>•\tPrepare and cook meals according to recipes and restaurant standards.</p><p>•\tEnsure all food items are properly stored, labeled, and rotated.</p><p>•\tMaintain cleanliness and organization of the kitchen, including workstations and equipment.</p><p>•\tFollow food safety and hygiene regulations to ensure compliance with health codes.</p><p>•\tAssist in menu planning and suggest new dishes.</p><p>•\tMonitor food stock and coordinate with kitchen staff for timely replenishment.</p><p>•\tWork as part of a team to ensure timely food preparation and customer satisfaction.</p><p>•\tAdhere to portion control and minimize food waste.</p><p>•\tAssist food preparation (chopping, washing, marinating)</p><p>•\tHelps in plating and garnishing dishes</p><p>•\tMaintains kitchen cleanliness and hygiene</p><p>Requirements:</p><p>•\tProven experience as a Cook or in a similar role.</p><p>•\tKnowledge of various cooking techniques and chinese cuisines .</p><p>•\tAbility to work efficiently in a fast-paced environment.</p><p>•\tStrong attention to detail and food presentation.</p><p>•\tNon-halal dishes (Pork)</p><p>Work Environment:</p><p>•\tFast-paced kitchen setting.</p><p>•\tStanding for long hours and working with hot equipment.</p><p>•\tCollaborative team environment.</p><p></p>",
