    "description": "<p>\r\n\t<strong>CHINA CONSTRUCTION REALTY CO. PTE. LTD.</strong></p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tCCR was established on January 2000 with BCA registered capital of 4.8 million. CCr had obtained certificates such as PHSMS, ISO 14000, ISO9000, Green & Gracious and etc. Currently CCR employs around 100 staffs and over one thousand workers.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tCCR is specialised in the construction of condominium projects. over the last 14 years, we have been building-up good relationships with a pool of reputable clients and specialists. In addition we have completed more than 30 projects such as condominium, commercial development, hotel and factory. Currently CCR is undertakes private projects namely Botanique, The Terrace EC, 70 Saint Patrick's, 18 Woodsville, M38 Factory, and etc.</p>\r\n",
